info.author: Stephen Vermeulen
info.description:
added excludedir filter to exclude some subdirectories
        from within the set of backup directories.  This is useful
        when backing up Visual C++ projects where you don't want the
        compiler output files (like .objs) to be backed up. Fixed a
        few bugs as well.
        See the release notes page for more 
        details: http://arcvback.com/arcvback_releasenotes.html
info.name: arcvback
info.summary: Backup software for a small LAN for user data files
info.html_description:
added excludedir filter to exclude some subdirectories
from within the set of backup directories. This is useful when backing up Visual C++ projects where you don’t want the compiler output files (like .objs) to be backed up. Fixed a few bugs as well. See the release notes page for more details: http://arcvback.com/arcvback_releasenotes.html
